webLinks.linkText: The Hills Shire Council road closures

properties.diversions: Cliftonville Rd, Wisemans Ferry Rd, Old Northern Rd.

properties.otherAdvice:
Kamilaroi Hwy from Walgett to Brewarrina is closed

Castlereagh Hwy 15km south of Walgett is closed to light vehicles
properties.diversions:
Bourke to Walgett: Mitchell Hwy to Dubbo, Newell Hwy to Gilgandra, Castlereagh Hwy to Walgett.

Brewarrina to Bourke Arthur Hall Vc Way to Coolabah, Mitchell Hwy to Bourke.

properties.otherAdvice: Other local roads in the Forbes Shire Council area may be closed due to flooding or affected by recent adverse weather. Visit the council's website for further information.

properties.headline: FLOODING COREEN Riverina Highway CLOSED between Federation Way and Bull Plain Road
properties.diversions:
Eastbound: Bull Plain Rd, Spring Dr and Federation Ave to Corowa, then Honour Ave to return to Riverina Hwy south of Lowesdale.

Westbound: Riverina Hwy and Hounour Ave to Corowa, then Spring Dr and Bull Plain Rd to return to the Riverina Hwy.

This diversion is suitable for all vehicles.

properties.otherAdvice: GARAH TO MUNGUNDI Carnarvon Highway is closed
MOREE TO GARAH Carnarvon Highway is closed

Closure due to current flood evacuation advice in Echuca.

Northbound will remain open.

There is a current flood evacuation advice in Echuca.

Local residents can use the bridge to travel in both directions

properties.headline: FLOODING DARLINGTON POINT TO COLLINGULLIE Sturt Highway CLOSED between Kidman Way and Lockhart Road
properties.diversions:
Westbound from Wagga Wagga: Olympic Hwy, Coolamon Rd, Canola Way and Newell Hwy to Narrandera. Then, Irrigation Way, Whitton Darlington Point Rd and Kidman Way.

Eastbound from Darlington Point: Kidman Way, Whitton Darlington Point Rd and Irrigation Way to Narrandera. Then, Newell Hwy, Canola Way Coolamon Rd, and Olympic Hwy to Wagga Wagga.

These diversions are suitable for heavy vehicles up to 25/26m B-Double only

properties.otherAdvice: The Kamilaroi Hwy is also closed between Gunnedah and Breeza.
The highway is also closed between Wee Waa and Merah North.
The highway is also closed from Wee Waa to Narrabri.

properties.headline: FLOODING JERILDERIE TO GILLENBAH (SOUTH OF NARRANDERA) Newell Highway between Kidman Way and Sturt Highway
properties.diversions:
Jerilderie to Narrandera: Kidman Way, Whitton Darlington Point Rd and Irrigation Way

Narrandera to Jerilderie: Irrigation Way, Whitton Darlington Point Rd and Kidman Way

Southbound from Wilcannia: Barrier Hwy to Cobar, Kidman Way to Goolgowi, and Mid Western Hwy to Hay.

Northbound from Hay: Mid Western Hwy to Goolgowi, Kidman Way to Cobar, and Barrier Hwy to Wilcannia.

This route is suitable for all vehicles and will add around 4hrs to your travel time.

Eastbound: Oxley Hwy to Nevertire, Mitchell Hwy to Dubbo, Newell Hwy to Gilgandra.

Westbound: Newell Hwy to Dubbo, Mitchell Highway to Nevertire to the Oxley Highway.

properties.headline: FLOODING FORBES TO GOOLOOGONG Lachlan Valley Way CLOSED
properties.otherAdvice: Lachlan Valley Way from Cowra to Gooloogong is open under alternating stop/slow traffic conditions.
properties.diversions:
Motorists to use Newell Hwy, Mid Western Hwy to travel between Cowra and Forbes.

This is suitable for all vehicles.

properties.headline: FLOODING COWRA TO JEMALONG (WEST OF FORBES) Lachlan Valley Way CLOSED at multiple locations

properties.otherAdvice: Road conditions for Unincorporated Area of the Western Region are available on 08 8082 6660.

properties.diversions: Motorists can exit the Motorway at Heathcote Rd or Hume Hwy.

properties.headline: FLOODING NARRABRI TO BOGGABILLA Newell Highway CLOSED
properties.otherAdvice: The Kamilaroi Hwy is also closed between Narrabri and Gunnedah.
properties.diversions:
Motorists can use the Castlereagh Hwy to travel between Gilgandra and the Queensland border via Walgett. Allow plenty of extra travel time.

This route is suitable for all vehicles including B-doubles and triples.

Wellington to Gulgong : Mitchell Hwy to Dubbo, Golden Hwy to Dunedoo, Castlereagh Hwy to Gulgong 

Gulgong to Wellington: Castlereagh Hwy to Dunedoo, Golden Hwy to Dubbo, Mitchell Hwy to Wellington

This diversion is suitable for all vehicles.

Light vehicles can divert via Saleyards Ln and Bell St in both directions.

Southbound heavy vehicles: From Dunedoo - Golden Hwy to Cassilis, then Ulan Rd to Mudgee

Northbound heavy vehicles: Ulan Rd to Cassilis, then Golden Hwy to Dunedoo.

properties.headline: FLOODING BOURKE TO GUNNEDAH Kamilaroi Highway CLOSED at multiple locations
properties.otherAdvice: The Kamilaroi Hwy is also closed from Brewarrina to Bourke.
properties.diversions:
From Brewarrina eastbound: Arthur Hall Vc Way to Coolabah, Mitchell Hwy to Dubbo, Newell Hwy to Gilgandra, Castlereagh Hwy to Walgett.

From Walgett westbound: Castlereagh Hwy to Gilgandra, Newell Hwy to Dubbo, Mitchell Hwy to Coolabah, then Arthur Hall Vc Way to Brewarrina.

Northbound from Gunnedah: Oxley Hwy to Coonabarabran, Newell Hwy to Narrabri.

Southbound from Narrabri: Newell Hwy to Coonabarabran, Oxley Hwy to Gunnedah.

Heavy vehicle diversion:

Southbound from Cowra: Olympic Hwy to Young, then Murringo Rd to Boorowa.

Northbound from Boorowa: Murringo Rd to Young, then Olympic Hwy to Cowra.


Light vehicles diversion

﻿Southbound from Cowra: Olympic Hwy to Morongla Rd, then Lachlan Valley Way to Boorowa.

Northbound from Boorowa: Lachlan Valley Way then Morongla Rd to Cowra.

properties.otherAdvice: Road conditions for Unincorporated Area of the Western Region are available on 08 8082 6660.
